# d2c74383fde448caaa82ad487ab325be
#: ../../developer-guide/api/functions/TSHttpTxnMilestoneGet.en.rst:37
msgid ""
":func:`TSHttpTxnMilestoneGet` will fetch a specific :arg:`milestone` "
"timer value for the transaction :arg:`txnp`. These timers are calculated "
"during the lifetime of a transaction and are measured in nanoseconds from"
" the beginning of the transaction. :arg:`time` is used a pointer to "
"storage to update if the call is successful."
